A man was murdered, and his wife seriously injured earlier this week in a robbery. CAPE TOWN - A youth was due to appear in court on Thursday in connection with a deadly attack on a couple at a Bonnievale farm. A man was murdered, and his wife seriously injured earlier this week in a robbery. The 19-year-old suspect will face charges of murder and attempted murder. More arrests were expected, as three suspects were still at large on Thursday. Apart from being stabbed, the 55-year-old woman was allegedly also tortured with boiling water during Monday night's attack. (Edited by Shimoney Regter)